06:35.298 --> 06:37.100
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

06:55.818 --> 06:59.153
DEB: Hey. So why Tahiti?
What brought you here?

06:59.155 --> 07:00.290
TAMI: The wind, I guess.

07:01.424 --> 07:02.656
