08:36.083 --> 08:37.951
Sorry, what was your name?

08:37.953 --> 08:40.086
- Richard.
- Richard, I'm Deb.

08:40.087 --> 08:41.355
Hi, Deb.

08:41.357 --> 08:42.325
This is Tami.

08:43.091 --> 08:44.092
Hey.

08:46.629 --> 08:47.829
Tami.

08:48.997 --> 08:50.264
Thank you.

08:50.266 --> 08:51.767
Yeah, no problem.

09:00.210 --> 09:01.211
See you.

09:01.678 --> 09:02.878
Nice to meet you.

09:03.246 --> 09:04.911
You too.

09:04.913 --> 09:06.416
See you around.

09:17.660 --> 09:19.861
(YAWNS)

09:52.794 --> 09:54.162
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)

