10:26.763 --> 10:28.464
I'm actually a vegetarian.

10:29.097 --> 10:31.197
- (LAUGHING) So...
- Right.

10:31.199 --> 10:32.633
I like them
when they're alive.

10:32.635 --> 10:33.933
- (BOTH CHUCKLE)
- I was gonna see

10:33.935 --> 10:37.039
if you just wanted
to grab an early dinner?

10:37.573 --> 10:38.874
Uh...

10:41.411 --> 10:42.543
But seeing as you're...

10:42.545 --> 10:43.411
Do you know what, I can make

10:43.413 --> 10:46.014
a really good
vegetarian version.

10:46.815 --> 10:49.317
That sounds great. (LAUGHS)

10:49.319 --> 10:51.752
- Good, good. Sold.
- Yes. Thank you.

10:51.754 --> 10:53.053
- (CHUCKLES)
- Done.

10:53.055 --> 10:55.991
Do you want me
to grab anything else?

10:57.493 --> 10:59.227
Uh, some vegetables?

11:00.162 --> 11:02.262
(LAUGHING)

11:02.264 --> 11:03.333
I can do that.

11:06.769 --> 11:08.636
TAMI: You've been
to so many places.

11:08.638 --> 11:09.737
So cool.

11:09.739 --> 11:10.805
RICHARD: Yep.

11:10.807 --> 11:11.905
