11:18.180 --> 11:21.615
when I was working in
a boat yard in South Africa.

11:21.617 --> 11:23.419
You built this boat?

11:23.985 --> 11:25.253
RICHARD: Mmm.

11:26.356 --> 11:27.655
That's a big deal.

11:27.657 --> 11:29.289
- That's so impressive.
- (LAUGHS)

