What's it like sailing
out there all alone?

11:56.552 --> 11:59.720
Uh... Miserable.

11:59.722 --> 12:01.356
- (CHUCKLES)
- Cold.

12:01.791 --> 12:03.356
Utterly awful.

12:03.358 --> 12:04.792
C'mon...

12:04.794 --> 12:06.126
- (CHUCKLES)
- Seriously?

12:06.128 --> 12:08.529
