12:40.530 --> 12:41.597
Uh...

12:43.633 --> 12:45.200
It... It's a feeling...

12:47.135 --> 12:49.404
A feeling I can't describe.

12:50.673 --> 12:53.074
Uh, it's intense.

12:54.075 --> 12:56.044
The infinite horizon.

12:58.280 --> 13:02.650
After a few days,
uh, I feel reborn.

13:02.652 --> 13:04.352
You know, just you,

13:05.721 --> 13:08.188
